body_html: @DakshMiglani All the files are uploaded to Google Drive. You can gain access from this link. The folder includes builds for major python versions like 2.7, 3.5 and 3.6. Due to lack of support for nvcc with mingw compiler, the 2.7 package is CPU-only. The pytorch packages are for Windows 10 and Windows Server 2016, while pytorch_legacy packages are for other legacy Windows versions.
